title: I didnt get my mystery champion
body: So it was ocean week or ever and i for sure contributed enough points, like 70, and my friend got his mystery champion but i didnt get mine so idk if it takes time for other people i already tried restarting my application, stilll no champion

replies.body:
Hey there,

The mystery champions are currently being rolled out in batches, if you're still yet to receive yours you will receive it soon.

These things take time, be patient young padawan.
